! Using JSON Convert

A complete guide to converting JSON into tiddlers with this plugin —
tutorial up front, reference toward the back.

The demo wiki has guided walkthroughs with screenshots:
<<doc-link "Profile Guide">>, <<doc-link "Console Guide">>, and
<<doc-link "Transforms Guide">>.  This Usage tiddler is the
reference — exhaustive, designed for looking things up rather than
learning from.  Reach for the guides first; come back here when you
want depth.

